Package: ansperf
Title: Operational Performance Analysis of Air Transportation / Air Navigation with R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Rainer",
           family = "Koelle",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "rainer.koelle@eurocontrol.int",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2810-1404"))
Description: The {ansperf} package supports the operational performance analysis
    of air transportation / air navigation. It is based on the performance indicators
    of ICAO's Global Air Navigation Plan and conventions made by the international  
    benchmarking community.
    Interested decision-makers, practitioners, and researchers are encouraged to 
    reuse and augment the functions and provide feedback.
